		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
		"name": "DoAnTotNghiep API v3 - BLOCKCHAIN INTEGRATION ✅",
		"description": "Collection kiểm thử đầy đủ tất cả Priority 1 + Priority 2 features:\n\n**Priority 1 Triển khai xong ✅**\n- Health Check & Auth (Register, Login, Logout)\n- Campaigns CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete)\n- Draft Mode (Create draft, Update draft, List drafts, Approve, Reject)\n- Role-Based Middleware (Admin, Staff, Beneficiary auth)\n- Message Queue (Redis + Bull - async webhook processing)\n- Off-Chain Donation Logic (Bank + Ethereum webhooks, deduplication, raised_amount sync)\n- Webhook Processing (Bank & Ethereum, idempotency, error handling)\n\n**Priority 2 Triển khai xong ✅**\n- Blockchain Integration (NEW - Section 7)\n  • Admin approves draft → Mint campaign on Besu blockchain\n  • DonationRecorded event listener → Process blockchain events\n  • Event deduplication & recovery mechanism\n  • Audit trail in blockchain_events table\n  • Graceful error handling (502 when blockchain unavailable)\n\n**Biến môi trường cần thiết:**\n- baseUrl: http://localhost:3000\n- authToken: JWT token từ login (auto-set bởi login endpoint)\n- campaignId: Campaign UUID (auto-set bởi create campaign)\n- draftCampaignId: Draft campaign UUID (auto-set bởi create draft)\n\n**Flow kiểm thử đề xuất:**\n1. Health Check (Section 1)\n2. Auth → Login để lấy token (Section 2)\n3. Create Campaign (Section 3)\n4. Create Draft & Approve (Section 5) → Blockchain mint sẽ triggered\n5. Webhooks & Queue (Sections 4 & 6)\n6. Blockchain Integration (Section 7) → Verify txHash stored + event processing",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "baseUrl",    "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
